    "ensemble": "All models combined. Best default pick. Can share the same blind spot.",
    "elo_baseline": "Standard sports betting baseline based on past wins/losses. Good long-run read. Slow on sudden changes.",
    "glm_ridge": "Linear pregame model anchored by projected rotation strength, matchup splits, rest, and absence pressure. It is only as good as the lineup view going into tipoff.",
    "glm_elastic_net": "Elastic-net pregame model using the same NBA linear feature map as ridge while allowing extra shrinkage on overlapping lineup and rating signals.",
    "glm_lasso": "Lasso pregame model using the NBA linear feature map with stronger pruning on overlapping lineup, rating, and availability signals.",
